import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Box, Typography, Button, Grid, Container } from '@mui/material';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar';
import './Home.css';

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container className="home-container">
      <Grid item xs={12} md={5} lg={4}>
        <Sidebar />
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={7} lg={8}>
        <Box className="content-container">
          <Container maxWidth="md">
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', py: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" component={Link} to="/" sx={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#3f51b5' }}>
                ðŸŽ‰ Eventify
              </Typography>
              <Box>
                <Button component={Link} to="/" color="primary">Home</Button>
                <Button component={Link} to="/about" color="primary">About us</Button>
                <Button component={Link} to="/contact" color="primary">Contact</Button>
              </Box>
            </Box>

            <Box sx={{ mt: 10, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom>
                Eventify - Makes every occasion special
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" color="textSecondary" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
                Plan, invite and celebrate with ease.
              </Typography>
              
              <Box sx={{ mt: 4, display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 2 }}>
                <Button 
                  variant="contained" 
                  color="primary" 
                  size="large" 
                  component={Link} 
                  to="/register"
                >
                  Sign Up
                </Button>
                <Button 
                  variant="outlined" 
                  color="primary" 
                  size="large" 
                  component={Link} 
                  to="/login"
                >
                  Login
                </Button>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Container>
        </Box>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
};

export default Home;
